					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13297543#post-4634149</guid>
				<title>The Jr. Staff Site Crit O&#039; Doom</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13297543/scp-3279#post-4634149</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2020 19:16:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>KaraKatt</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5950867</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Hello hello!</p> <p>I’m Kara from the Site Crit team!</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Oh&nbsp;yes</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I want to start by saying that I don't think there's much for me to crit here! You did a really good job, and this is really interesting and cool!</p> <p>- I'm a little confused on what SCP-3279-1 is. Is it the house that constantly changes from the last? It reads like that, though I thought it was just one house?</p> <p>Honestly, that's it. That's all I could find that stuck out to me. Great job Popsioak! This made me want to draw some fan art, and honestly, if I could achieve collapsible in collapsible you would see it here. I can not say how much of a good job you did.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p><span style="font-size:smaller;"><em><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Opinions expressed in this review do not reflect the opinions of SCP Wiki staff as a whole. Please respond to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karakatt" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5950867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1588910437" alt="KaraKatt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5950867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/karakatt" >KaraKatt</a></span> or contact the captain of the Site Criticism Team, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1588910437" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" >SoullessSingularity</a></span>, for any questions or concerns relating to this review</em></span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
