					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13297543#post-4634076</guid>
				<title>North By North.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13297543/scp-3279#post-4634076</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2020 18:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Popsioak</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5231418</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <hr /> <blockquote> <p><span style="color:green">Like this piece? See it and many more saplings like it, at Popsioak's Garden, <a href="http://scp-wiki.net/popsioaks-garden" target="_blank">here!</a></span></p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ynP-URuXOy0">soft sound so soothing</a></strong></em><br /> <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ynP-URuXOy0">something that sits so deep in the back of your head</a></strong></em><br /> <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ynP-URuXOy0">while you’re asleep</a></strong></em><br /> <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ynP-URuXOy0">i caught you running, for something so far away</a></strong></em><br /> <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ynP-URuXOy0">knowing you could not spend another day</a></strong></em><br /> ~~ <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5jkfpDNgg6U">(knowing you cannot not stay forever)</a></strong></em> ~~</p> </blockquote> </div> <hr /> <blockquote> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/almarduk" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3672751&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589660581" alt="Almarduk" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3672751)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/almarduk" >Almarduk</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brewsterion-1017" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3093017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589660581" alt="Brewsterion 1017" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3093017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brewsterion-1017" >Brewsterion 1017</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4646198&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589660581" alt="BlueJones" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4646198)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" >BlueJones</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wolfen32" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3508684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589660581" alt="Wolfen32" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3508684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wolfen32" >Wolfen32</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/voct" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=392303&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589660581" alt="Voct" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=392303)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/voct" >Voct</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5271378&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589660581" alt="Mew-ltiverse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5271378)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mew-ltiverse" >Mew-ltiverse</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1989312&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589660581" alt="Doctor Fullham" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1989312)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" >Doctor Fullham</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/trustyolvalet2" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5366711&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589660581" alt="TrustyOlValet2" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5366711)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/trustyolvalet2" >TrustyOlValet2</a></span> for polish and critique.</p> </blockquote> <p>No accompanied listening for this one. It's really rooted in my own Sikh beliefs here; of life after death, stories of swans diving into lakes and emerging &quot;pure,&quot; of people dying and leaving behind only fresh flowers. Partition hit my own grandfather hard; the rivers divided, that sort of thing. It's also a bit of a personal way to deal with some things going on.</p> <p>image creds below :)<br /> images</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:AB071_Merionis_hurrianae.JPG">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:AB071_Merionis_hurrianae.JPG</a></p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
